name: We Have Come Into This Place
chorusText:
(G)
We have come into this place To gather in His name
And worship Him
Worship Him, Jesus Christ, our Lord.
Let us lift up Holy handsMagnify His name
And worship Him.
Worship Him, Jesus Christ our Lord.
So forget about yourselvesConcentrate on Him and worship Him
Worship Him, Jesus Christ our Lord.
